snippet.textDisplay:
I can't seem to do certain things right, even though I try to avoid them and be careful, but it's hard to resist making simple but stupid or embarassing mistakes sometimes.

Because of that and add to the fact that I have a better time remembering the bad memories than the good ones and I tend to mentally punish myself a little bit for my occasional screw ups.

I've never been on a date in my entire 29 year-old life and I'm worried that if I did finally did get a date with a guy that I'd just screw it up or have trouble remember the good times and that I would never fall in love.

I'm worried that I'll never find true love and or know the whole meaning of this song and what it feels like.
